          //p.nh-txt-intro During the <em>Corona Lockdown 2020</em> I came up with this personal mini project: <em>Lockdown Portraits</em>, showing real people – not models – and how they deal with all the ordeals that isolation brings with it. Accompanying the photos are 2 questions I asked each one of them and their answers.
